      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "he went down to Ahab to Samaria; to pay him a visit upon the alliance, civil and matrimonial, contracted between them: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Ahab killed sheep and oxen for him in abundance, and for the people that he had with him; entertained him and his retinue in a very grand and liberal manner: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and persuaded him to go up with him to Ramothgilead; from hence, to the end of the chapter, it is the same with 1 Kings 22:4. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
