        "text": "). In ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 18:31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", after the words, \"and Jehoshaphat cried out,\" the higher cause of Jehoshaphat's rescue is pointed out in the words, \"and Jahve helped him, and God drove them from him,\" which are not found in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
